                <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-3x mb-3 text-secondary"></i>
                <h3 class="fw-bold">Data Analytics</h3>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Leverage real-time data to monitor your solar system’s performance. Our analytics platform delivers actionable insights,
                    helping you optimize energy output, reduce costs, and anticipate maintenance needs.
                </p>
                <a href="/data-analytics" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2: Cloud-Based Data Solutions -->
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex mb-4">
            <div class="service-card p-4 shadow rounded w-100 d-flex flex-column">
                <i class="fas fa-cloud fa-3x mb-3 text-secondary"></i>
                <h3 class="fw-bold">Cloud-Based Data Solutions</h3>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Securely store and manage your solar performance data in the cloud.
                    Access comprehensive reports and system metrics from anywhere, ensuring your solar operations are always optimized.
                </p>
                <a href="/cloud-solutions" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3: Energy Management Systems -->
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex mb-4">
            <div class="service-card p-4 shadow rounded w-100 d-flex flex-column">
                <i class="fas fa-bolt fa-3x mb-3 text-secondary"></i>
                <h3 class="fw-bold">Energy Management Systems</h3>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Optimize your energy consumption with smart management systems that integrate renewable power with grid support.
                    Our solutions help you reduce energy costs while maximizing efficiency and sustainability.
                </p>
                <a href="/energy-management" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Section Continued -->
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <!-- Service 4: Solar Data Visualization Tools -->
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex mb-4">
            <div class="service-card p-4 shadow rounded w-100 d-flex flex-column">
                <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt fa-3x mb-3 text-secondary"></i>
                <h3 class="fw-bold">Solar Data Visualization Tools</h3>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Transform complex solar performance metrics into clear, actionable insights.
                    Our interactive dashboards make it easy to track energy production, monitor system health, and plan for the future.
                </p>
                <a href="/data-visualization" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 5: Solar Panel Monitoring Solutions -->
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex mb-4">
            <div class="service-card p-4 shadow rounded w-100 d-flex flex-column">
                <i class="fas fa-solar-panel fa-3x mb-3 text-secondary"></i>
                <h3 class="fw-bold">Solar Panel Monitoring Solutions</h3>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Ensure your solar panels operate at peak performance with our robust monitoring solutions.
                    Receive real-time alerts and detailed diagnostics to safeguard your investment and extend your system’s lifespan.
                </p>
                <a href="/panel-monitoring" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 6: Custom Solar Solutions -->
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex mb-4">
            <div class="service-card p-4 shadow rounded w-100 d-flex flex-column">
                <i class="fas fa-cogs fa-3x mb-3 text-secondary"></i>
                <h3 class="fw-bold">Custom Solar Solutions</h3>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    Tailored to meet your unique energy needs, our custom solar solutions integrate expert design, installation,
                    and maintenance. Whether it’s for residential or commercial applications, we deliver reliable and efficient renewable energy.
                </p>
                <a href="/custom-solar-solutions" class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
