    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold text-secondary">Let's Power the Future Together</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
            Contact us today to explore how our innovative solar energy solutions can transform your energy operations and drive sustainability.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get in Touch</a>
